occurred on my disks L-3, L-4.

250
00:11:49,087 --> 00:11:52,063
Nothing, you know,
a little rest stretching...

251
00:11:52,188 --> 00:11:54,504
Maybe a good massage
will just kick it right out.

252
00:11:54,672 --> 00:11:58,008
Intervertebral disk degeneration
shouldn't be taken lightly.

253
00:11:58,176 --> 00:12:00,298
Are you wearing
your lumbo-sacral support belt?

254
00:12:00,423 --> 00:12:01,423
Yeah,

255
00:12:01,606 --> 00:12:03,847
a girdle, you mean.
Yes, it's nice and tight.

256
00:12:04,228 --> 00:12:05,438
Oh, hold on.

257
00:12:07,649 --> 00:12:09,685
- It's Booth.
- Hey, it's Perotta.

258
00:12:09,810 --> 00:12:11,855
How you doing?
You need anything?

259
00:12:12,023 --> 00:12:14,303
No. I am just dandy.

260
00:12:14,787 --> 00:12:16,284
Well, if you do...

261
00:12:17,636 --> 00:12:18,987
